header.abouthead
  .overlay
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-12
        h1
          span About
        hr
.container-even
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-7.event-text
        h3 Shaping international culture at ASU
        p
          | Coalition of International Students or CIS is one of the 7 identity/cultural based coalitions at Arizona State University that forms the Council of Coalitions. Within CIS is 19 partner organizations registered within Arizona State University as members of cultural, identity-based and/or diversity based student organizations.
          br
      .col-md-5
        img.img-fluid(src='assets/cis-glo-ball-night-0006.JPG')
.container-odd
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-12.nested-title
        p our audience
      .col-md-4.numbers-text
        h2 CIS serves individuals from all parts of the world.
      .col-md-8
        .row
          .col-md-6.numbers
            h1 6000+
            p people reached across our events throughout the academic year
          .col-md-6.numbers
            h1 40+
            p dedicated students leaders in our team helping daily operations
          .col-md-6.numbers
            h1 19
            p partner organizations consisting of identity/cultural orgs
          .col-md-6.numbers
            h1 3
            p signature events throughout the academic year
.container-even
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-12.nested-title
        p our events
      .col-md-12
        p
          | Throughout the academic year, we as a coalition hold several events to not only promote our presence on campus but to provide international students with the opportunity to interact with other students and make ASU their home.
      .col-md-4
        img.img-fluid(src='assets/cis-international-night-0013.JPG')
      .col-md-4
        img.img-fluid(src='assets/cis-glo-ball-night-0009.JPG')
      .col-md-4
        img.img-fluid(src='assets/cis-international-night-0012.JPG')
      .col-md-3
        .row
          .col-md-12.event-name
            h2 International
            h2
              b Night
          .col-md-12.event-descrip
            p
              | our biggest event is also asu's most cultural event promoting understanding between different cultures. takes place every november.
            a.btn.btn-outline-dark.btn-sm(href='events.html#in') Learn more
      .col-md-3
        .row
          .col-md-12.event-name
            h2 Glo-Ball
            h2
              b Night
          .col-md-12.event-descrip
            p
              | our closing event for each academic year to celebrate the success of the outgoing year. also celebrating the partnerships of our partners.
            a.btn.btn-outline-dark.btn-sm(href='events.html#gbn') Learn more
      .col-md-3
        .row
          .col-md-12.event-name
            h2 Career
            h2
              b Conference
          .col-md-12.event-descrip
            p
              | a platform specifically tailored for international students to gain valuable information before the hiring season takes full blow.
            a.btn.btn-outline-dark.btn-sm(href='events.html#cc') Learn more
      .col-md-3
        .row
          .col-md-12.event-name
            h2 Welcome
            h2
              b Carnival
          .col-md-12.event-descrip
            p
              | an introductory event targeted towards new international students to welcome them to the asu community.
            a.btn.btn-outline-dark.btn-sm(href='events.html#wc') Learn more
.container-odd
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-12.nested-title
        p our partners
      .col-md-12
        p
          | Everything we do would not be possible without the support of our partner organizations. Interested in being part of our network? 
          a(href='contact.html') Contact us
          |  for more information
      .col-md-12
        table.table.table-bordered.table-hover.table-condensed.partner-table
          tbody
            | {% for partner in site.data.partner-orgs %}
            tr
              td {{ partner.name }}
              td
                center
                  a(href='{{ partner.url }}', target='_blank')
                    i(class='{{ partner.class }}')(style='color:{{ partner.color }}')
                    |  {{ partner.type }}
            | {% endfor %}
.container-even
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-12.nested-title
        p our team
      .col-md-12
        p
          | all of this would not be possible without the amazing support from our rising students leaders that chose to dedicate their time to CIS.
        center
          a.btn.btn-outline-primary.btn-sm(href='team.html') Learn More
